[This is the 1st report of violence against polio vaccination teams in the Philippines. The involved area is in MIndinao. While there haven't been polio cases reported from Kitcharao municipality, the Mindinao region has been where the cVDPV2 activity has been occurring in the Philippines. This doesn't bode well for the ongoing olio vaccination efforts in the region.

A map showing the provinces of the Philippines can be found at https://www.mapsofworld.com/philippines/philippines-political-map.html. - Mod.MPP]
